casebody.data:
Monday, March 20, 1995

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-385. No. 93-G-1827. L & M Properties Co. v. Shanker. Geauga County,

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
